        "timestamp": "2018-02-26 12:30:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nMunir, the issue here is AAI model-loader tried to connect to DMaaP, although DMaaP was not up. At some point, AAI give up trying, hence remain in a bad state. Bouncing AAI once DMaaP is up fixes the issue. A proper fix would be to prevent starting AAI model-loader if DMaaP is not up.\nAlso, based on the logs in the JIRA, what you've changed here very not related. The logs aren't saying localhost, they are targetting one of the external ip of K8S hosts, which is correct.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
