        "timestamp": "2018-02-26 13:29:58.000000000",
        "message": "Abandoned\n\nYou are right I was surprised why would it make a difference when switching from local host to k8s namespace but it worked after I made that change. I guess side effect/restart of the pod was the actual fix.",
